      "content": "got it. so if i'm looking at the Dinka and the Nuer specifically, is it safe to assume their conflict is basically an inherent part of their culture or way of life, or is it more of a recent thing caused by the government? just trying to figure out if this is something we can actually work around or if it's just how things are there.",
